\c 18
\s Ukwabiwa kwelizwe eShilo
\p
\v 1 Inhlangano yonke-ke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli yabuthana eShilo\x + 18.8-10. 19.51; 21.2; 22.9,12. Hlu. 18.31; 21.12,19,21. 1 Sam. 1.3,9,24; 2.14; 3.21; 4.3,4,12; 14.3. 1 Kho. 2.27; 14.2,4. Hlab. 78.60. Jer. 7.12,14; 26.6,9; 41.5. Josh. 16.6.\x*, yamisa khona ithente lenhlangano. Lelizwe lalehliselwe phansi phambi kwabo.
\v 2 Kwasekusele phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli izizwe eziyisikhombisa ezazingabelwanga ilifa lazo.
\v 3 UJoshuwa wasesithi kubantwana bakoIsrayeli: Koze kube nini lidonda ukuyakudla ilifa lelizwe\x + Hlu. 18.9.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyihlo elinike lona?
\v 4 Zinikeni amadoda amathathu ngesizwe, ngiwathume, asukume ahambe adabule ilizwe, alibhale ngokwelifa lazo, abuye kimi.
\v 5 Azalehlukanisa libe yizabelo eziyisikhombisa; uJuda\x + 15.1.\x* uzahlala emngceleni wakhe eningizimu, labendlu kaJosefa\x + 16.1,4.\x* bahlale emngceleni wabo enyakatho.
\v 6 Lani lizabhala ilizwe ngezigaba eziyisikhombisa, beseliletha kimi lapha, ukuthi ngiliphosele inkatho lapha phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu\x + 14.2.\x*.
\v 7 Ngoba amaLevi kawalasabelo phakathi kwenu\x + 13.33. Nani 18.20.\x*, ngoba ubupristi beN\nd kosi\nd* buyilifa labo. LoGadi\x + 13.8.\x* loRubeni lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase sebethethe ilifa labo ngaphetsheya kweJordani empumalanga, uMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyabanika lona.
\p
\v 8 Asesuka amadoda ahamba. UJoshuwa wawalaya ahambayo ukubhala ilizwe esithi: Hambani lidabule ilizwe lilibhale, libuyele kimi, ukuze ngiliphosele inkatho lapha phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* eShilo.
\v 9 Ngakho amadoda ahamba adabula phakathi kwelizwe, alibhala ngemizi ngezigaba eziyisikhombisa egwalweni; asebuya kuJoshuwa enkambeni eShilo.
\v 10 UJoshuwa wasebaphosela inkatho eShilo phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; uJoshuwa wasebabela lapho ilizwe abantwana bakoIsrayeli ngokwezigaba zabo\x + 11.23; 12.7.\x*.
\s Ilizwe elanikwa isizwe sakoBhenjamini
\p
\v 11 Inkatho yesizwe sabantwana bakoBhenjamini yavela ngokwensendo zabo. Lomngcele wenkatho yabo waphuma phakathi kwabantwana bakoJuda labantwana bakoJosefa.
\v 12 Lomngcele wabo ngenyakatho wasukela eJordani\x + 16.1.\x*, lomngcele wenyuka ewatheni leJeriko enyakatho, wasusenyuka udabula entabeni usiya entshonalanga, lokuphuma kwawo kwaba senkangala\x + 16.1.\x* yeBeti-Aveni\x + 7.2.\x*.
\v 13 Lomngcele wedlula usuka lapho waya eLuzi, ewatheni leLuzi, eyiBhetheli\x + 16.2.\x*, ngeningizimu; lomngcele wehlela eAtarothi-Adari\x + 16.5.\x*, eduze lentaba engeningizimu kweBhethi-Horoni\x + 10.10.\x* engaphansi.
\v 14 Umngcele wagoba-ke, waphenduka waya eceleni lentshonalanga ngeningizimu, kusukela entabeni emaqondana leBhethi-Horoni\x + 10.10.\x* eningizimu; lokuphuma kwawo kwaba eKiriyathi-Bhali, eyiKiriyathi-Jeyarimi\x + 9.17.\x*, umuzi wabantwana bakoJuda. Lolu luhlangothi lwentshonalanga.
\v 15 Lohlangothi lweningizimu lusephethelweni leKiriyathi-Jeyarimi; lomngcele waphuma waya entshonalanga, waphuma waya emthonjeni wamanzi weNefitowa\x + 15.9.\x*.
\v 16 Umngcele wasusehla usiya ephethelweni lentaba emaqondana lesihotsha sendodana kaHinomu esisesihotsheni seziqhwaga enyakatho\x + 17.15.\x*, wasusehlela esihotsheni seHinomu\x + 15.8. 2 Kho. 23.10. 2 Lan. 28.3; 33.6. Jer. 7.31,32; 19.2,6; 32.35.\x* ewatheni lamaJebusi eningizimu, wehlela eEni-Rogeli\x + 15.7.\x*;
\v 17 wagoba usukela enyakatho waphuma eEni-Shemeshi\x + 15.7.\x*, waphumela eGelilothi emaqondana lomqanso weAdumimi\x + 15.7.\x*, wehlela elitsheni likaBohani indodana kaRubeni\x + 15.6.\x*;
\v 18 wadlulela ewatheni maqondana leAraba enyakatho, wehlela eAraba.
\v 19 Umngcele wasusedlulela ewatheni leBeti-Hogila enyakatho\x + 15.6.\x*, lokuphuma komngcele kwakusethekwini loLwandle lweTshwayi enyakatho, ephethelweni leJordani ngeningizimu. Lo ngumngcele weningizimu.
\v 20 LeJordani ingumngcele walo ehlangothini lwempumalanga. Leli yilifa labantwana bakoBhenjamini ngemingcele yalo inhlangothi zonke, ngokwensendo zabo.
\p
\v 21 Lemizi yesizwe sabantwana bakoBhenjamini ngokwensendo zabo yile: IJeriko\x + 18.12. 2.1.\x* leBeti-Hogila\x + 15.6.\x* leEmeki-Kezizi
\v 22 leBeti-Araba\x + 15.6.\x* leZemarayimi\x + Gen. 10.18. 2 Lan. 13.4.\x* leBhetheli\x + 16.2.\x*
\v 23 leAvimi lePara leOfira\x + 1 Sam. 13.17. Mika 1.10.\x*
\v 24 leKefari-Amoni leOfini leGeba\x + 21.17. 1 Sam. 13.3,16. Ezra 2.26. Neh. 7.30; 11.31. Isa. 10.29.\x*; imizi elitshumi lambili lemizana yayo.
\v 25 IGibeyoni\x + 9.3.\x* leRama\x + Hlu. 4.5; 19.13. 1 Sam. 22.6. 1 Kho. 15.17,21. 2 Lan. 16.1,5. Ezra 2.26. Neh. 7.30; 11.33. Isa. 10.29. Jer. 31.15,40.1. Hos. 5.8. Mat. 2.18. 1 Sam. 1.19.\x* leBeyerothi\x + 9.17. Ezra 2.25.\x*
\v 26 leMizipa\x + Hlu. 20.1,3; 21.1,5,8. 1 Sam. 7.5,6,16; 10.17. 2 Kho. 25.23. Josh. 15.38.\x* leKefira\x + 9.17. Ezra 2.25.\x* leMoza
\v 27 leRekemi leIripheyeli leTarala
\v 28 leZela\x + 2 Sam. 21.14.\x*, iElefi, leJebusi\x + 18.16. 15.8,63.\x*, okuyiJerusalema, iGibeyathi\x + Hlu. 19.12-16; 20.4. 1 Sam. 10.26; 11.4; 13.15; 14.16; 15.34; 22.6. 2 Sam. 21.6; 23.29. 1 Lan. 11.31; 12.3. Isa. 10.29. Hos. 5.8; 9.9; 10.9.\x*, iKiriyathi\x + Ezra 2.25.\x*; imizi elitshumi lane lemizana yayo. Leli yilifa labantwana bakoBhenjamini ngokwensendo zabo.